oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Robert's Western World Home of Traditional Country Music (2008)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Advertising; Robert's Western World (Nashville, Tenn.); Restrikes;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and orange on brown) announcing Robert's Western World, home of traditional country music, on Broadway in Nashville, Tennessee. Poster features woodcuts of cowboy boots and a guitar. This poster was reprinted in 2011, 2013 and 2015. Posters printed after the original edition are known as "restrikes."
